    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some typical wear-and-tear sounds and a less-than-perfect idle. The exterior has several visible scratches, some minor dings, and the paint has faded in certain spots, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, functional vehicle who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
