      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your adventures! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully\u2014perfect if you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
