      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS for exceptional throttle response across the power band. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, transferring power through a torque-sensing M-variable differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the subframe has been proactively inspected. While showing signs of honest road use, the mechanical integrity is robust, with the rod bearing service and valve clearances recently addressed. This is a mechanically sound example ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
